Package: plop
Title: A 'ggplot2' assistant
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Simon", "Couch", , "simon.couch@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5676-5107")),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Provides an interactive addin that helps users iterate on ggplot2
    code. Given some code selection from your editor, the assistant will
    iteratively generate a plot, suggest changes to make it more informative, 
    and then incorporate suggestions into a new plot.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
